snippet.title: The Sims 3 Showtime Producer Walkthrough
snippet.description: Live the rags to riches story with your Sims as a singer, acrobat, magician... and moonlight as a DJ. Learn more about the upcoming release of The Sims 3 Showtime as our producers walk you through how you can share the story of your Sims' rise to fame! Coming to PC Expansion Pack on March 6, 2012.
